es everything; the time for performing good deeds has passed away, and death is nearing, and actions are weakening, hopes have reached the point of hopelessness, and the time to shift towards the Hereafter has arrived.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "یَا مَن یَّعْلَمُ هَوَاجِسَ السِّرَائِرِ، وَمَكَامِنَ الضَّمَائِرِ، وَحَقَائِقَ الْخَوَاطِرِ، یَا مَنْ هُوَ لِكُلِّ غَیْبٍ حَاضِرٌ، وَلِكُلِّ مَنْسِیٍّ ذَاكِرٌ، وَعَلٰی كُلِّ شَیْءٍ قَادِرٌ، وَاِلَی الْكُلِّ نَاظِرٌ، بَعُدَ الْمَهَلُ، وَقَرُبَ الْاَجَلُ، وَضَعُفَ الْعَمَلُ، وَاَرَابَ الْاَمَلُ، وَآنَ الْمُنْتَقَلُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, 