ed the friends of Allah and distanced himself from them, and regarded their rights to be of his own.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَحَلُّوَا فِیْ حَیْرَۃِ الْمَحَجَّۃِ وَهُمْسِ الضَّجَّۃِ، مَعْدُوْلٌ بِهِمْ عَنِ الْمَحَجَّۃِ اِلَّا مَنْ سَبَقَتْ لَهٗ مِنَ اللهِ الْحُسْنٰی، فَنَجَا مِنْ هَوْلِ الْمَشْهَدِ وَعَظِیْمِ الْمَوْرِدِ، وَلَمْ یَكُنْ مِّمَّنْ فِی الدُّنْیَا تَمَرَّدَ، وَلَا عَلٰی اَوْلِیَائِ اللهِ تَعَنَّدَ، وَلَهُمُ اسْتَبْعَدَ، وَعَنْهُمْ بِحُقُوْقِهِمْ تَفَرَّدَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "Ara